node.text:
my concert film “Happier Than Ever: A Love Letter To Los Angeles” is out now on @disneyplus 🥰 it was such an honor to work with so many amazing and talented people on this and celebrate this city that i love so much. it was such a full circle moment 💘 and so cool getting to perform my entire album front to back for you at the one and only @hollywoodbowl. i cannot wait to be with you again SO SO SOOOOON. love you all so so much and hope you enjoy 🤍 watch now at link in bio 🕊

@rodriguez @posborne @finneas @gustavodudamel @laphil @lachildrenschorus
